name: Mata Ariki - The Wayfinder's Love part I
description: Solace; the artwork is depicted in many observations before you, from the flow of timespace weaving through her hair, to the gravitational waves that exist around her being, her korowai (cloak) adorns the energy of countless rebirths of stars in the universe.  she is constant but she is always changing.  Based upon Maori lore of Matariki/Matariki the many stories that surround a group of 9 stars in a cluster that form her, a Maori new year.  Created and recorded in real-time.
